body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>He answered beginner\'s questions in an easy-to-understand manner.<br />Thank you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Best E-commerce Solution for Me</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/d88pak/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3315ee331e8b4284ab1919996a9ed256?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3315ee331e8b4284ab1919996a9ed256?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/d88pak/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Deepak <small>(d88pak)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 14, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I have tried other e-commerce platforms. Either the learning curve is too steep or some are simply too expensive with monthly recurring charges.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WooCommerce is the no-nonsense e-commerce solution that gave me a head start from the day one.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I highly recommend WooCommerce for anyone starting an e-commerce business.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Best plugin for everyone for e-commerce website</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/skyler007/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/504900975ccf7aaa6dccd0edd2f3edd6?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/504900975ccf7aaa6dccd0edd2f3edd6?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/skyler007/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">skyler007</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 13, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Woocommerce is good for every e-commerce website. I manage all things easily throung this plugin.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Plugin, Amazing Support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/onabhani/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5e1c0e6dd7598fef0ad4ba63312b7dd5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5e1c0e6dd7598fef0ad4ba63312b7dd5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/onabhani/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Omar <small>(onabhani)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 13, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nothing to say here, it is WooCommerce with its great support team! </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Problemas con la visualización de productos</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/merchemg/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c1a55f02b9f3e55d547e23e31af2f10f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c1a55f02b9f3e55d547e23e31af2f10f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/merchemg/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">merchemg</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 12, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Se ven las categorías y subcategorías, pero los productos NO</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good salessystem, very good support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/vdub_nl/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/131bdbd2172dd30e54509cf1628c96dd?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/131bdbd2172dd30e54509cf1628c96dd?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/vdub_nl/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Vdub_nl</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 12, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I use Woocommerce for different sites, sometimes there are some minor issues and mostly they can be solved through customer support!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph